Code
N=4
Tasks: (2,100), (1,19), (2,27), (1,25)
Sort by profit → (2,100), (2,27), (1,25), (1,19).

Task (2,100) → slot 2 free → schedule.

Task (2,27) → slot 2 taken → slot 1 free → schedule.

Task (1,25) → slot 1 taken → skip.

Task (1,19) → slot 1 taken → skip.

Profit = 127, Tasks = 2 ✅

🎯 Revision Hook
When revising:

“Job Sequencing” → Sort by profit → Greedy slot allocation.”

Always try to place task in the latest free slot ≤ deadline.

👉 Memory trick:
“Biggest profit first, push it as late as possible.”
